OL,3,CUK's housing stock 'offers the worst
OL,4,Cvalue for money of any advanced
OL,5,Ceconomy'
OL,7,FThe UK's "expensive, cramped and
OL,8,Fageing" housing stock fares poorly
OL,9,Fcompared with other advanced
OL,10,Fcountries, analysis by a think tank
OL,11,Fsuggests.
OL,13,FHouseholds are paying more than other
OL,14,Fcountries ` but getting less in
OL,15,Freturn, the Resolution Foundation said.
OL,17,FIts report said: "When it comes to
OL,18,Fhousing, UK households are getting an
OL,19,Finferior product in terms of both
OL,20,Fquantity and quality."
