OL,4,Cvalue for money of any advanced
OL,5,Ceconomy'
OL,7,FThe UK's housing stock is also
OL,8,Frelatively old, with 38% of homes
OL,9,Fbuilt before 1946, the report said,
OL,10,Fcompared with around a fifth (21%) in
OL,11,FItaly and one in nine (11%) in Spain.
OL,13,FOlder homes can be poorly insulated,
OL,14,Fleading to higher energy bills and a
OL,15,Fhigher risk of damp, according to the
OL,16,FFoundation, which is focused on
OL,17,Fimproving the living standards for
OL,18,Fthose on low to middle incomes.
