OL,7,FThe report said: "If all households in
OL,8,Fthe UK were fully exposed to our
OL,9,Fhousing market, they would have to
OL,10,Fdevote 22% of their spending to
OL,11,Fhousing services, far higher than the
OL,12,FOECD average (17%), and the highest
OL,13,Flevel across the developed economies
OL,14,Fwith the solitary exception of
OL,15,FFinland."
