OL,7,FAdam Corlett, principal economist at
OL,8,Fthe Resolution Foundation, said:
OL,9,F"Britain's housing crisis is likely to
OL,10,Fbe a big topic in the election
OL,11,Fcampaign, as parties debate how to
OL,12,Faddress the problems of high costs,
OL,13,Fpoor quality and low security that
OL,14,Fface so many households.
