OL,3,CUK's housing stock 'offers the worst
OL,4,Cvalue for money of any advanced
OL,5,Ceconomy'
OL,7,F"Britain is one of many countries
OL,8,Fapparently in the midst of a housing
OL,9,Fcrisis, and it can be difficult to
OL,10,Fseparate rhetoric from reality. But by
OL,11,Flooking at housing costs, floorspace
OL,12,Fand wider issues of quality, we find
OL,13,Fthat the UK's expensive, cramped and
OL,14,Fageing housing stock offers the worst
OL,15,Fvalue for money of any advanced
OL,16,Feconomy.
