OL,7,F"At the same time as increasing the
OL,8,Fquantity of homes we are driving up
OL,9,Fquality, with the number of non-decent
OL,10,Fhomes down by two million since 2010.
OL,12,F"Our landmark Renters Reform Bill is
OL,13,Fprogressing through Parliament and
OL,14,Fwill give tenants more security in
OL,15,Ftheir homes, while our #11.5 billion
OL,16,Finvestment in the affordable homes
OL,17,FProgramme and #1.2 billion local
OL,18,Fauthority housing fund will help build
OL,19,Fa new generation of affordable and
OL,20,Fsocial housing."
